<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Confirmation Letter</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Confirmation Letter</h1>
    <p>Dear {{full_name}},</p>

    <p>
      We are delighted to confirm your permanent employment with us as a
      <strong>{{stack}}</strong>. Your contributions since your joining on
      <strong>{{date_of_joining}}</strong> have been highly appreciated.
    </p>

    <p>
      We look forward to your continued dedication and growth within the organization.
    </p>

    <p>
      Congratulations on this significant milestone!
    </p>

    <p>Best regards,<br/>HR Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Metaphi Pvt. Ltd. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>